body:
I'm trying to start my own node. But it's not finished after weeks. I checked with api

```sh
curl -H "content-type:application/json" -X POST --data '{"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"eth_syncing","params":[],"id":1}' localhost:8545 | jq
```

